            Laboratory Notes

			      Subject: Patient X-132

    		    Researcher: Dr. Emil Spon

			      Immersion #XX Results

            The immersion was a complete success today. Patient X eventually opened up, not only about the crime, but about the motivation behind it.
            Subsequent questioning revealed the location of the sabotage, deep in the heart of the capitol city. It was quickly subverted, much to
            our relief. Had the device activated, it would have resulted in the deaths of thousands of our good citizens.

            Patient X has been removed by Dark Agency personnel. We were not directly informed of what was to be done next, but I have learned through
            unofficial channels that an execution will occur shortly.

            Long live our glorious nation!

> day 1

